Constructor Detail

GraphSesameNBIM

public GraphSesameNBIM(boolean sync,
                       String dir)
Create a Jena Graph, which represents a Sesame double repository which uses an in-memory one for performance and a native one for persistence. This is non-inferencing.

Parameters:
sync - the the Sesame repository is synchronized or not.
dir - specifies the directory that can be used by the native sail to store its files.
